**** Notes ***

round corners: "img-flud rounded"

padding: "img-fluid p-2"

round image: "img-fluid rounded-circle"

border: "img-fluid border"

shadow: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm

ex: <div class="container"> 
    <img src=images/picture.jpg"
    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm p-2 border"

grid margins: mb-3 
remove if you want it on top of eachother 
ex: <div class=col-sm-4 mb-3>
computer screen: x x x
phone screen: x
              x
              x




*** Responsive using CSS - without bootstrap ***

<style>
img {
max-width: 100%;
height:auto;
} 


